					      //    GRADARAN    //

FUNCTION SPEC

I_book_system	  // ays system-i ognutyamb mer cragir@ petq e kapvac lini mi qani haytni kayqeri het vorpeszi inet-i arkayutyan 			     depqum download ani ayn nyuter@ voronq avelacvel en tvyal kayqerum
Book_Section      // Book_Section-@ mez hnaravorutyun kta dasavorel grqer@ @st mer cankutyan ev kognen user-in aravel hesht exanakov 			     gtnel ayn inch@ inq@ pntrum e searching_systemi ognutyan
searching system  // ays system-@ hnaravoutyun kta user-in hnaravorins hesht gtnel iren hetaqrqrox voreve nyut
sign_in system    // ays system@ hnaravorutyun e talis grancvel ev darnal ogtater mer online gradaranum inch@ hnaravorutyun e talis 			     upload anel aynpisi girq vor@ chka mer gradaranum, inchpes nayev patvirel motaka xanutneric
video_lesson      // video_lesson-@ canotacnum e user-in cragri ev nranic ogtvelu kargi het (miayn arajin angam)


development spec

I_book_system

1. ete mer hamakargich@ kpac che inet-in uremn mer cragri mej menq kunenanq miayn cragri stexcman pahin download exac grqeri cank@
2. isk inet-i arkayutyan depqum inq@ kstugi ete kan norutyunner mer het kap hastatac kayqerum anmijapes download kani dranq

Book_Section

  // mer cragir@ kunena 10 entabajin tarber lezunerov,  voronc mej el grqer@ dasavorvac klinen @st hexinakneri (aybenakan kargov)
1. Haykakan grqeri entabajin
2. Russian books section
3. English books section
4. Spanish
5. German
6. Italia
7. France
8. Chine
9. George
10.Holand

searching system

  // mer cragrum hnaravor klini search anel @st hexinaki anvan, @st grqi vernagri, @st grqi entagluxneri vernagreri kam aravel       	  haytni u taracvac barakapakcutyunnerov (ays sur@ vor@ spanec davajan hor@ kspani nayev uracox mor@)
1. searching @st hexinaki
2. searching @st grqi vernagri
3. searching @st grqi gluxneri vernagri
4. searching @st barakapakcutyunneri

sign_in system
  
  // grancveluc heto ogtater@ stanum a aravelutyunner chgrancvac useri hamemat
  // grancveluc heto ogtatiroj@ trvum e ir arandzin gradaran@ voroshaki hishoxutyan cavalov
1. na karox e ir gradaran upload anel ayn inch kuzi
2. na karox e ogtvel voroshaki aravelutyunneric, baci girq pntrel@, download ev upload anel@ na karox e nayev girq patvirel,         	patvirelu depqum vjarum@ katarvum e bankain classic qarteri mijocov
3. na karox e ogtvel searching system-i aravelutyunneric, grancvac ogtatereri hamar searching katarvum e voch miayn cragri nersum    	ayl nayev online (karox en tesnel te irenc pntrac grqic moataka xanutneric vor mekum ka ev inch arji)
4. aktivutyan tokosner@ mer nshac sandxakin hascnelu depqum ogtater@ karox e ogtvel zexchain hamakargic petveri depqum

video_lesson

  // ete uzer-@ chi cankanum ditel viseo-lesson-@ uremn nran hnaravorutyun e trvum pakel ayd ej@ (inch@ xorhurd chi trvum)

implement product 

